graph TD
    User([用户]) --> WebUI[Web UI<br/>FastAPI + Jinja2 + TailwindCSS]

    WebUI --> SearchAPI[搜索 API<br/>POST /search]
    WebUI --> ResultsAPI[结果 API<br/>GET /results]
    WebUI --> FilterAPI[筛选 API<br/>GET /filter]

    SearchAPI --> RateLimiter[频率限制器]
    RateLimiter --> SearchService[搜索编排服务]

    SearchService --> JDScraper[京东爬虫<br/>Playwright stealth]
    JDScraper --> JDSearch[京东搜索页]
    JDScraper --> JDDetail[京东详情页]

    SearchService --> HTMLParser[HTML 解析器<br/>BS4 + lxml]
    SearchService --> ImageDL[图片下载器]
    SearchService --> OCRService[OCR 服务]

    OCRService --> Ollama[Ollama API]
    Ollama --> QwenVL[Qwen2.5-VL<br/>本地多模态 LLM]

    OCRService --> IngredientParser[配料文本解析器]

    SearchService --> DB[(SQLite)]
    ResultsAPI --> DB
    FilterAPI --> DB

    ImageDL --> LocalFS[/本地文件系统<br/>data/images//]

    subgraph 数据模型
        SearchTask[SearchTask<br/>搜索任务]
        Product[Product<br/>商品信息]
        Ingredient[Ingredient<br/>配料信息]
        SearchTask --> Product
        Product --> Ingredient
    end

    DB --> 数据模型
